data.name: verticalLabel_makedir.ToolTip
data.value: Create new folder on Android device

data.name: checkBox_android6fix.ToolTip
data.value: Enabling this fixes some compatibility issues with Android 6 and older devices

data.name: checkBox_preview.ToolTip
data.value: When file is double clicked, it will copy it to temp folder and display it. On program close the files will be deleted

data.name: checkBox_android6fix_fastmode.ToolTip
data.value: Will speed up dir load times in compatibility mode, at the cost of smaller accuracy of folder icons

data.name: checkBox_unwrapfolders.ToolTip
data.value: The progress bar during copying is updated only when a whole file or a directory gets copied, so when copying large directory the progress bar is unresponsive and may freeze. This will "unwrap" the directories into individual files so the copy appears smoother
